  "description": "<i>Kurushi Final: Mental Blocks</i> is a puzzle game where your wits are pitted against a 'higher power'. It is the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/intelligent-qube\">Kurushi</a>.<br><br>Standing on an isolated platform, you must destroy blocks that are rolling towards you in order to survive.  By destroying certain blocks, the size of the platform increases. If blocks fall off the edge of the platform, or you destroy the incorrect blocks, the platform becomes smaller.<br><br>There are four game modes: 100 Attack, Survival, Create and Final.  It has nine  player characters (1 Initial, 8 Hidden) and includes a facility to create custom levels.<br><br>",
